title: Bug 4121 JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: Bug 4121 JarExporter causes out of Sync.
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported JAR in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time.
EB: The out of sync message should not be displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time.
SR:
1. Open the project in the software.
2. Export the directory as a JAR file.
3. Place the exported JAR file in the same directory (project).
4. Overwrite the exported JAR file.
5. Repeat step 4 and observe if the out of sync message is displayed.
